      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 10:55:40 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;script src=&#34;https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.min.js&#34; integrity=&#34;sha256-ZosEbRLbNQzLpnKIkEdrPv7lOy9C27hHQ+Xp8a4MxAQ=&#34; crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=http://localhost:1313/js/load-photoswipe.js&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=&#34;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/photoswipe/4.1.1/photoswipe.min.css&#34; integrity=&#34;sha256-sCl5PUOGMLfFYctzDW3MtRib0ctyUvI9Qsmq2wXOeBY=&#34; crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=&#34;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/photoswipe/4.1.1/default-skin/default-skin.min.css&#34; integrity=&#34;sha256-BFeI1V+Vh1Rk37wswuOYn5lsTcaU96hGaI7OUVCLjPc=&#34; crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/photoswipe/4.1.1/photoswipe.min.js&#34; integrity=&#34;sha256-UplRCs9v4KXVJvVY+p+RSo5Q4ilAUXh7kpjyIP5odyc=&#34; crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/photoswipe/4.1.1/photoswipe-ui-default.min.js&#34; integrity=&#34;sha256-PWHOlUzc96pMc8ThwRIXPn8yH4NOLu42RQ0b9SpnpFk=&#34; crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pswp&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34; role=&#34;dialog&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pswp__bg&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pswp__scroll-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__container&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__item&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__item&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__item&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__top-bar&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__counter&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--close&#34; title=&#34;Close (Esc)&#34;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--share&#34; title=&#34;Share&#34;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--fs&#34; title=&#34;Toggle fullscreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--zoom&#34; title=&#34;Zoom in/out&#34;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__preloader&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__preloader__icn&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__preloader__cut&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__preloader__donut&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidden pswp__single-tap&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__share-tooltip&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--left&#34; title=&#34;Previous (arrow left)&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button class=&#34;pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--right&#34; title=&#34;Next (arrow right)&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__caption&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;pswp__caption__center&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Dod â natur yn fyw. ID bywyd gwyllt, creu cynefinoedd a gweithdai adrodd straeon i greu Stori Wyllt.&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;Bring nature to life. Wildlife ID, habitat creation &amp;amp; storytelling workshops to create a Wild Story.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mae Stori Wyllt yn brosiect peilot ar gyfer ysgolion cynradd yng Cheredigion sy&amp;rsquo;n rhedeg o fis Mawrth i fis Mehefin 2026, gyda&amp;rsquo;r nod o ymgorffori adferiad natur ym mywyd yr ysgol, wedi‘i drefnu gan &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.naturceredigion.cymru/cy/&#34;&gt;Bartneriaeth Natur Ceredigion&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;Stori Wyllt is a pilot project for primary schools in Ceredigion running from March to June 2026, aiming to embed nature recovery into school life, organised by &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.naturceredigion.cymru/en/&#34;&gt;Ceredigion Nature Partnership&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ysgol Llanarth Workshop 1</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/260327-llanarth-workshop-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 15:50:24 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/260327-llanarth-workshop-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NB:&lt;/strong&gt; The notes before Easter have been written in retrospect, which means they lack detail. In future, I’ll be writing notes immediately afterwards, and also asking for immediate &amp;amp; short feedback from students and participants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This workshop was a riot, in the best sense of the word! I made a quick introduction about Stori Wyllt but I was a bit worried about the rain, so we headed off to Molly‘s field Cae Ysgubor. The route is via a public bridleway by the side of the nursery and campsite. However, it was &lt;em&gt;very&lt;/em&gt; wet, with some localised flooding! The path also turned muddy going uphill, with some surface water. But everyone seemed very positive.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
